---
layout: layouts/base.njk
title: AI 生态田野札记
description: "Openflows（开流）关于开源 AI 生态系统的长篇田野札记、综合与分析。"
lang: zh
permalink: /zh/blog/
---

<section class="hero-panel">
  <div>
    <p class="hero-kicker">田野札记</p>
    <h2>AI 生态田野札记</h2>
    <p>这里的文章越过周期性摘要，展开对开源 AI 基础设施、治理实践与生态张力的较长篇幅观察。</p>
  </div>
  <div class="stat-grid">
    <div class="stat"><strong>{{ collections.zh_blog.length }}</strong><span>中文文章</span></div>
    <div class="stat"><strong>{{ collections.blog.length }}</strong><span>英文文章</span></div>
  </div>
</section>

<div class="filter-bar">
  <label>
    <span class="muted">筛选</span>
    <input type="search" id="blog-filter" placeholder="按标题、主题或摘要筛选..." autocomplete="off">
  </label>
</div>

{% if collections.zh_blog.length %}
<ul class="currency-list blog-list">
  {% for item in collections.zh_blog %}
  <li data-blog-item>
    {% if item.data.heroImage %}
    <a href="{{ item.url }}" class="blog-list-image">
      <img src="{{ item.data.heroImage }}" alt="{{ item.data.heroImageAlt or '' }}">
    </a>
    {% endif %}
    <div>
      <a href="{{ item.url }}">{{ item.data.title }}</a>
      {% if item.data.abstract %}
      <p class="item-abstract">{{ item.data.abstract }}</p>
      {% endif %}
      <div class="item-meta">
        <span class="muted">{{ item.date | readableDate }}</span>
        {% set itemTopics = item.data.topics or [] %}
        {% for topic in itemTopics %}
        <span class="chip">{{ topic }}</span>
        {% endfor %}
      </div>
    </div>
  </li>
  {% endfor %}
</ul>
{% else %}
<section class="section-band">
  <p>暂无中文田野札记。已审阅并发布的中文博客译稿会显示在这里。</p>
</section>
{% endif %}

<script>
(function() {
  const input = document.getElementById('blog-filter');
  if (!input) return;
  const items = document.querySelectorAll('[data-blog-item]');
  input.addEventListener('input', function() {
    const q = this.value.toLowerCase();
    items.forEach(function(li) {
      li.style.display = li.textContent.toLowerCase().includes(q) ? '' : 'none';
    });
  });
})();
</script>
